changelog:
Initial release of Minecraft Mage modpacks:

**Client Pack:**
- Performance mods (Sodium, Iris)
- UI improvements (EMI, Jade, Mod Menu)
- Quality of life features
- AutoSwitch support

**Server Pack:**
- Server optimization (Lithium, Starlight)
- Admin tools (LuckPerms, Essential Commands)
- Monitoring (Spark, BlueMap)
- Carpet mod for technical features
- AutoSwitch server support
